# Project Description
Create a simple task management application with the ability to add, edit, delete, and filter tasks. The application should be responsive, ergonomic, and aesthetically pleasing.

# Project Main Features

## 1. Task Registry
- Display task list with information:
  - Title
  - Description
  - Status (e.g., "To Do", "In Progress", "Done")
- Ability to mark tasks as completed

## 2. Task Management
- Form for adding new tasks (title, description, status)
- Edit existing tasks (e.g., via "Edit" button)

## 3. Filtering and Sorting
- Search tasks by description and title text
- Filter tasks by status
- Sort by creation date (ascending/descending)

## 4. Task Deletion
- Ability to remove tasks from the list

## 5. Responsiveness
- UI adapted for mobile devices and desktops

## 6. Additional Features
- Task statistics and analytics
- Export/Import functionality
- Task reminders and notifications
- Collaborative features (future scope)
- Task templates
- Custom task fields
- Task history and audit log

## 7. Secondary Features
- Form validation (e.g., empty field checks)
- Debounce mechanism for task text search
- Animations for adding/removing tasks
- Unit tests for key functions (e.g., adding/editing tasks)
- Ability to switch task list view between list and card layouts
- Dark mode with toggle switch